{"tid":285984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來係台灣販運693公斤毒品就已經稱為「史上最大宗」！","createTime":"2017-06-16T09:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T07:31:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec51de7d68bebce8af00f774bb6bd394ff752da3","tid":285984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"台狗都未見過700噸鴉片係點樣<br />\n693公斤？ 笑死人咩！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nownews.com/n/2017/05/28/2541138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fn%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F2541138&d=fMdE%2FihnzDatPyQN0%2FGRLwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6f8a200e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nownews.com/n/2017/05/28/2541138</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=800&amp;q=60&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2F9a%2F06%2F9a06a11af53c7b5ce46ea04576444d5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D800%26q%3D60%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fs.nownews.com%252F9a%252F06%252F9a06a11af53c7b5ce46ea04576444d5f.jpg&h=b043ae57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲高雄地檢署指揮海巡第二機動查緝隊，在烏坵東南約12.5浬海域，登船查獲一艘東港籍的漁船涉嫌走私運輸第一級毒品海洛因1800塊，初估總毛重約693公斤，市值近百億元。（圖／記者宋德威攝，2017.5.28）<br />\n<br />\n日前高雄地檢署指揮海巡、警方破獲國內史上最大宗海洛因走私案，今(28)日上午，行政院長林全南下高雄地檢署行政大樓大禮堂，出席「查獲歷年來最大宗海洛因毒品走私案」記者會。該案件為烏坵東南方海域攔截漁船「永富升號」，涉嫌運毒1800塊高純度海洛因磚，重達693公斤，黑市價格破百億，許姓、邱姓、2名郭姓台籍船員共4人今午遭法院裁定羈押禁見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=720&amp;q=60&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/186939/hash/75/21/75214925503f7dca34b3205b026bb615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D720%26q%3D60%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F186939%2Fhash%2F75%2F21%2F75214925503f7dca34b3205b026bb615.jpg&h=79c76f30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1091cf59e485305de969df4e2c77dc11c7da76bb","tid":285984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"台狗講乜野TAIWAN NO. 1？<br />\n<br />\n問過香港未？"},{"pid":"309f876036a9a680b6fb752314433dfb02add7bb","tid":285984,"uid":19267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"馬生潛逃去台灣定居 嚴格嚟講都係台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb27077eb830fd73aaa27beb685d22236b34df1","tid":285984,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"486710d00d9102fd0098d9934b3dce32c6057af0","tid":285984,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6a7d93fbbdd5872707b2de6350c935bc5a7848","tid":285984,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac0be4f149f93b7b867a1b66a54366fe3912c6d","tid":285984,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76e498c1726c23a83e3b52d990239b4c3cd396fe","tid":285984,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"[quote]台狗都未見過<span style=\"color: red;\">700噸鴉片</span>係點樣<br />\n693公斤？ 笑死人咩！<br />\n<br />\n邊單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6556c36fb4695a74c0402af2c58e56e52edb3325","tid":285984,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台狗都未見過<span style=\"color: red;\">700噸鴉片</span>係點樣<br />\n693公斤？ 笑死人咩！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊下香港禁毒處就知啦！"},{"pid":"9885f58dc4f9339e4d8acbe47c89aa7913524acd","tid":285984,"uid":36414,"like":0,"di